The activations will begin in about a week. It will be an ongoing project, so the CDN could be activated on your site(s) at any time over the coming weeks.

Is the Kinsta CDN right for your site?

Most websites benefit from using a CDN, so we encourage everyone to take advantage of those benefits. But if your site uses technology or configuration that may be incompatible with a CDN, you can opt-out of activation in MyKinsta: Sites > sitename > Kinsta CDN.

Not sure whether a technology or configuration you use is compatible? Feel free to contact us, and we can take a look.

If you decide that you don't want to use the Kinsta CDN after it's enabled and active on your site, you can disable it on the Kinsta CDN page in MyKinsta.

Questions? Please don't hesitate to get in touch. We're here to help!
The Kinsta Team
